OL,6,FThe TV licence fee is set to rise by
OL,7,F#5.50 from #174.50 to #180 from April
OL,8,F1, the Department for Culture, Media
OL,9,Fand Sport (DCMS) has announced.
OL,11,FThe price increase will equate to an
OL,12,Fextra 46p a month, which is larger
OL,13,Fthan last year's rise of #5.
OL,15,FDCMS said the price hike was
OL,16,Fcalculated in line with the consumer
OL,17,Fprice index (CPI) until the end of the
OL,18,FBBC's Charter Period, which ends in
OL,19,F2027.
