OL,6,FThe annual cost of a black and white
OL,7,FTV licence will also increase by #2
OL,8,Ffrom #58.50 to #60.50 for 2026/27.
OL,10,FThe change forms part of the
OL,11,FGovernment's Charter Review Green
OL,12,FPaper public consultation on options
OL,13,Ffor the BBC's future funding.
OL,15,FThe DCMS said it wants to "support the
OL,16,Fgrowth of the Welsh creative
OL,17,Findustries" after it announced the
OL,18,FWelsh language channel S4C, which
OL,19,Freceives all its public funding from
OL,20,Fthe licence fee, would be receiving
OL,21,Faround #100 million in 2026/27.
